The paper discusses the development of a system called S-Store that combines stream processing and transaction processing. This work involves the integration of a traditional OLTP system with a simple transaction model for streams. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DB (Databases), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
